snippet.title: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Apology Video Mashup The Simpsons | Pillow Talk TV
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard's crazy Australian apology mashup with The Simpsons when Bart received public shaming from the Australian government for smuggling a frog. One happened on The Simpsons, the other is real. Both are wild punishments for barely a crime. 

Johnny Depp and Amber Heard apologize for traveling with their dogs. Bart Simpson refuses. Don't tread on me.
